I love the movies. The 1 star is for the bad copy. The sound doesn't work when playing the movie. The sound works on the previews. I checked our sound system and tried it with the same results. Don't buy it! you cant hear it!
Our boys love this series.  Great Martin Lawrence movies for movie night.  Kids loves them and able to enjoy by entire family members.
All the movies in the collection are funny, entertaining and well done.  They can be watched over and over and still be funny.  Good clean humor.  I recommend them for all family members.
